<P>
   Here is the CoxNet budget for papers of Monday, July 13. This
budget will be updated at 6 p.m. EDT and afterwards as necessary
based on news developments. A separate sports budget will move at 5
p.m. EDT.
</P>
<P>
   For questions after 5 p.m., the main CoxNet line is
404-526-5429.
</P>
<P>
   THE WEEKEND DUTY EDITORS ARE:
</P>
<P>
   IN ATLANTA: Paul Foutch at 770-509-1284 or (pager) 404 779-8620.
</P>
<P>
   IN WASHINGTON: Andy Glass at 202-363-2389.
