Canadian-originated preferred securities due 2097, Ba3/BBB/---.
Merrill Lynch &AMP; Co.
</P>
<P>
   Sovran Acquisition LP, $75 million of senior notes due in 2005,
Baa3/---/---. Paine Webber.
</P>
