<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-NBAF-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Atlanta plays host to National Black Arts Festival
 &HT;    By Steve Dollar and Sonia Murra
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
