jersey T-shirt with Raul Mondesi's number _ is a bit
presumptuous?...
</P>
<P>
   We can't wait four more years for the next World Cup. Maybe
eight, possibly 12, but not four....
</P>
<P>
   If this is what we've come to in the NBA lockout _ NBA stars
having to wrestle for money _ David Stern has no other choice but
to... I dunno... call his cable operator and order it up like
everyone else....
