   &UR; THE AMERICAS &LR;  &QC; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; `OTTAWHAAA!': CITIZENS OUTRAGED BY CHRETIEN'S `NEW OTTAWA'
SCHEME &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
