<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-12 22:41 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1467 &Cx1f; tta-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SOC-WORLDCUP-1STLD-WR     07-12 0882
